      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 angulation (5° lordotic angle) due to resource constraints. A second angulation condition was not tested, resulting in achieved level below required. This gap is acknowledged; the single condition represents the worst-case loading scenario per published literature, partially mitigating the shortfall."
