      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions mapped directly to experimental fixture geometry from engineering drawings. Applied displacement rate confirmed quasi-static (0.1 mm/s; inertial effects < 0.1% of peak force). Specimen geometry in FEA derived from same CMM data used for dimensional inspection of test articles."
