      "rationale": "All three primary QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria. E/uval values of 0.83, 1.41, and 1.09 all below 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences of 4.2%, 7.8%, and 6.1% all below 10% threshold. Comparison performed using pooled experimental uncertainty from both laboratories."
